img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"有無汗都要飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75b0f328ed830d7958f1b89e790b41e2d224fad","tid":2070831,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:36:36.000Z","msg":"原發性多汗症是原因不明的過度流汗，特點是過度出汗超過了正常體溫調節的生理需要。"},{"pid":"44d32964554a8a5b63e79d6268cc47abf583e18c","tid":2070831,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發覺肥仔特別大汗"},{"pid":"0400b1f465cf73128157a4f1bb11c2d26303f8fe","tid":2070831,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>原發性多汗症是原因不明的過度流汗，特點是過度出汗超過了正常體溫調節的生理需要。</del></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭汗多（包含面部流汗多）從醫學名稱來講叫做<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">頭汗症</span></strong>，僅僅是頭部（面部汗多）汗多影響了不少人的工作學習生活。有部分人群屬於容易出汗多但是頭面部汗特別多還有部分人僅僅是頭面部多汗。如何判斷是否病態，這隻要是不管任何情況下出汗多影響了您的生活就需要及時診療。常見的原因比如天熱，緊張，還有飲食後出汗多等。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/health/lj4pvz.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhealth%2Flj4pvz.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=c96324cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/health/lj4pvz.html</a>"},{"pid":"88362b8db9f0cd0b0d27cbe7579bb7fcfb1d2004","tid":2070831,"uid":216810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"我個頭無咩汗， 但係膊頭以下就揸得水出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e157089183124c8514543e0928bf13a847cae9a","tid":2070831,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"係咪日日洗頭同現在個頭笠唔笠真係有密切關係？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係咁嚴重，你出門前洗一次其實都只係減緩左小小"},{"pid":"b10f728b06de6e7af0ddf5868a4c344de7e96f97","tid":2070831,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim